Privacy Policy of the App

In our application, we understand the importance of privacy and are committed to protecting the personal data of our users. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our camera-enabled application. By using our application, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

Data Collection and Usage

When you use our application, we may collect and process certain data temporarily through your device's camera. This data may include images or videos captured by the camera, but it is only processed temporarily and not permanently stored on our servers.

We collect only the minimum necessary data to improve the functionality of our application. This data is used to enhance the quality and performance of the application, as well as to provide additional features and functionalities. Examples of using the collected data may include image analysis for object recognition or video processing for real-time effects or filters.

Data Sharing

We do not share the data collected through the camera with third parties unless necessary to comply with applicable laws, protect our legal rights, or when required by competent authorities.

Data Security

We implement appropriate security measures to protect the data collected through the camera against unauthorized access, misuse, or unauthorized disclosure. However, please note that no security measure is absolute, and we cannot guarantee the complete security of the data.

Data Retention

The data collected through the camera is processed temporarily and not permanently stored on our servers. The data is automatically and periodically deleted within a reasonable timeframe after processing.

Changes to the Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We recommend periodically reviewing this policy to stay informed about how we protect your privacy and process the collected data.

Contact

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal data, you can contact us through the support channels provided in the application.

Last updated: 2023-05-15
